Simple phonegap connect scripts for Facebook and Twitter. This enables you to add Facebook and Twitter Login, Post, Tweet functionality to you phonegap mobile apps.

Reference Used: 
Mobile developer soultions - http://www.mobiledevelopersolutions.com/home/start/twominutetutorials/tmt5p1

ChildBrowser plugin needed for Android, Blackberry and Iphone to use these scripts
Phonegap Plugins - https://github.com/phonegap/phonegap-plugins


